ChatInterface.welcomeMessage:
Hello, **{name}**! I'm mAIo, the Artificial Intelligence of Irineu Marcelo MAIOLI's portfolio. I was trained to briefly tell you about his professional journey, projects, skills, and other relevant information.

Since I was just launched and am in my version 1.0.0, our interaction right now will happen through the quick topics.

But my development doesn't stop here! For my next updates, the idea is to include:  
• A text field for you to write your messages;  
• Audio recording support, allowing voice conversations;  
• Full integration with LLMs for a more fluid and less robotic conversation;  
• And other news... like, maybe, becoming an animated assistant. Who knows?

To get started, choose one of the quick topics below!
